Boot machine with network switch off.  Start switch.  Networking is
dead.  Can't ping in or out.  Cannot telnet or anything else in.
[root@aurora quantumdot]# ifdown eth0
[root@aurora quantumdot]# ifup eth0
SIOCSIFFLAGS: No such device
SIOCADDRT: Network is down
Mine is a netgear with the real DEC chip in it.  I hope this helps debug
it.
